#

Creamy Ranch Dressing

5 min
$3.5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

DairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Condiment

Tags:

DressingDipCondiment

Description

A rich and tangy dressing perfect for salads, veggies, or as a dip.

Ingredients

  • mayonnaise: 1 cup
  • sour cream: 1/2 cup
  • buttermilk: 1/2 cup
  • dried dill weed: 1 teaspoon
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • onion powder: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/4 teaspoon
  • fresh chives (optional): 1 tablespoon, chopped
